    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"a beautiful kind of freedom\"... i guess. it just feels heavy. like, if everyone is just caught up in their own little bubbles, then there's actually no weight to my life. no impact. if i was gone, it wouldn't be a tragedy, it would just be... a quiet space where a person used to be. does that make sense?",
